data.description: Come check out this spacious 4 bed/2 bath home located in Kingsland, Georgia before it's too late! Here you'll find a master bath with a large soaking tub, plenty of kitchen cabinet space, a screened in porch, fenced in back yard and a 2 car garage. Not only are you just minutes from the interstate, this house also is just a 10 min drive to Kingsbay Naval Base or a twenty minute drive to Yulee, Fl. Call for a tour today- this place won't last long!
